OL,3,CParents of 11-year-old boy who drowned
OL,4,Cwarn against open water swimming
OL,6,FThe parents of Mackenzie Swift, who
OL,7,Fdrowned during the last heatwave, are
OL,8,Fcampaigning for greater water safety
OL,9,Fawareness before the summer holidays.
OL,11,FWords by North of England Reporter Amy
OL,12,FWelch and Northern Producer Georgia
OL,13,FLangdon
OL,15,FThe parents of an 11-year-old boy who
OL,16,Fdrowned during the last heatwave are
OL,17,Fpleading with other children to keep
OL,18,Fout of the water.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
