OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782398898
OL,3,CParents of 11-year-old boy who drowned
OL,4,Cwarn against open water swimming
OL,6,FFrom September, all children will be
OL,7,Ftaught water safety as part of the
OL,8,Fnational curriculum.
OL,10,FBut with the summer holidays looming,
OL,11,FMackenzie's parents are sharing his
OL,12,Fstory because they fear those lessons
OL,13,Fwill come too late.
